--- In nbwrpg@y..., robertdahl <rdahl@t...> wrote:
> Megatron looked at them, "How do you feel, about a fight?" Megatron
> asked, begining to head towards the elevator.

::DOMNIJOE AND BLINDCHAOS::

    The femme and the triple changer followed their leader eagerly.
    "Fighting is my life!!" Domnijoe said smartly and shook her fist 
forcefully in the air. "Give me a cause and I'll defent it for you 
Lord Megatron."
    Blindchaos was less enthusiastic, but he kept his real emotions 
hidden.
    "I'll do as ordered, Megatron." he said calmly, his smile forced.
